Two-Nine-Nine, huh?

252
00:14:37,083 --> 00:14:38,875
She's something else.

253
00:14:38,958 --> 00:14:40,083
So, the plan--

254
00:14:40,166 --> 00:14:41,500
Go!

255
00:14:41,583 --> 00:14:43,916
[GINOZA] We'll back
up the Inspector!

256
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,500
[KITAZAWA yells]

257
00:14:47,833 --> 00:14:50,750
[KITAZAWA] What's the
problem? Shoot me already!

258
00:14:50,833 --> 00:14:53,000
Isn't that the
right thing to do?

259
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:56,625
[AKANE] I won't shoot you.
Because if I do it right now,

260
00:14:56,708 --> 00:14:59,208
the Dominator will kill you.

261
00:14:59,833 --> 00:15:01,291
[KOMISSA]
Your attention, please.

262
00:15:01,375 --> 00:15:03,500
This is the Criminal
Investigation Department...

263
00:15:03,583 --> 00:15:06,208
[GINOZA] Everyone,
get out of here! Now!

264
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:07,458
Let's move!

265
00:15:07,541 --> 00:15:10,083
Hey! Remain calm and orderly!

266
00:15:10,166 --> 00:15:11,666
Why do I have to do this?

267
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,166
[KOMISSA] ...and exit
in an orderly fashion.

268
00:15:13,250 --> 00:15:16,250
[AOYANAGI] Ginoza!
What are you doing?

269
00:15:16,333 --> 00:15:17,708
We're supposed
to be hunting down

270
00:15:17,791 --> 00:15:19,833
and eliminating the suspect.

271
00:15:19,916 --> 00:15:21,875
Tsunemori is...

272
00:15:21,958 --> 00:15:24,208
[GINOZA] trying something
different tonight.

273
00:15:25,041 --> 00:15:27,208
[GINOZA] Think you can give
her a pass for the time being?

274
00:15:27,291 --> 00:15:31,083
You know, for not
going by the book on this?

275
00:15:31,166 --> 00:15:33,208
You sure changed.

276
00:15:33,291 --> 00:15:35,583
Of course. I've worked
with her a long time.

277
00:15:35,666 --> 00:15:37,041
It's natural.

278
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:40,583
[KUNIZUKA] Ginoza! A Division
Two Enforcer is moving

279
00:15:40,666 --> 00:15:42,041
to the building next door.

280
00:15:42,125 --> 00:15:43,500
[GINOZA] Got it.

281
00:15:44,583 --> 00:15:46,083
Hey, wait!

282
00:15:46,166 --> 00:15:47,625
Now what?

283
00:15:52,083 --> 00:15:55,625
[MIKA] So, that's what she
meant by "Two-Nine-Nine."

284
00:15:55,708 --> 00:15:58,166
I can't believe her.
An Inspector should not be

285
00:15:58,250 --> 00:15:59,791
making up their own rules.

286
00:15:59,875 --> 00:16:01,458
If you shut out those
you disagree with

287
00:16:01,541 --> 00:16:04,041
or close your eyes and try
to pretend they aren't there,

288
00:16:04,125 --> 00:16:06,333
you'll only end
up regretting it.

289
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:08,625
[GINOZA] Learn to
accept what's happening

290
00:16:08,708 --> 00:16:10,333
in front of your nose as fact.

291
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:13,541
That's a little shortcut
to adulthood. Okay, Missy.

292
00:16:24,083 --> 00:16:25,083
[KITAZAWA gasps]

293
00:16:25,166 --> 00:16:26,833
Stay back!

294
00:16:31,083 --> 00:16:34,000
We're all just puppets
being manipulated by Sibyl!

295
00:16:34,083 --> 00:16:35,666
We're slaves to the System!

296
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:37,958
[KITAZAWA] Don't you
think that's messed up?

297
00:16:38,708 --> 00:16:40,583
[KITAZAWA] No free
will! Our potential,

298
00:16:40,666 --> 00:16:42,416
our futures decided for us!

299
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:45,208
Only a select few benefiting
at all from this racket!

300
00:16:45,291 --> 00:16:47,041
Well, what does that
make the rest of us, huh?

301
00:16:47,125 --> 00:16:49,500
Worthless garbage
to be tossed aside?

302
00:16:49,583 --> 00:16:53,125
[AKANE] No. That's not
true. You have value!

303
00:16:53,208 --> 00:16:56,291
You serve a purpose and
so do those bombs you made!

304
00:16:56,375 --> 00:16:59,583
Are you crazy?
Why would you say that?

305
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:03,625
[AKANE] Society doesn't
always do the right thing.

306
00:17:03,708 --> 00:17:05,708
Which is why we ourselves

307
00:17:05,791 --> 00:17:08,583
have to lead virtuous lives.

308
00:17:09,666 --> 00:17:11,625
[KITAZAWA] But I--

309
00:17:11,708 --> 00:17:14,458
[AKANE] Your innate desire
to right systemic wrongs,

310
00:17:14,541 --> 00:17:16,750
not to mention
your technical skills.

311
00:17:16,833 --> 00:17:19,625
Those are things
society needs more of.

312
00:17:19,708 --> 00:17:22,083
Society isn't
some monolithic beast.

313
00:17:22,166 --> 00:17:24,583
It's made up of
individuals like you.

314
00:17:24,666 --> 00:17:26,458
By simply living
a virtuous life,

315
00:17:26,541 --> 00:17:29,666
you move society towards
the path of virtue.

316
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:33,083
I admire your sense
of justice. It's noble.

317
00:17:33,166 --> 00:17:36,000
[SAKUYA] You're more than
just a cog in the machine.

318
00:17:36,083 --> 00:17:38,333
Even when society
pressures you,

319
00:17:38,416 --> 00:17:40,416
as long as you resist it...

320
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:43,958
you can remain
human. Just stay strong.

321
00:17:44,041 --> 00:17:46,208
[AKANE] Mr. Togane.

322
00:17:48,875 --> 00:17:51,458
What the hell are
they waiting for?

323
00:17:51,541 --> 00:17:53,666
[DOMINATOR] Target is
a registered Enforcer.

324
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:56,125
Status, enforce at will.

325
00:17:56,666 --> 00:17:58,250
Hm.

326
00:17:59,875 --> 00:18:02,583
[AOYANAGI] Put the gun down!

327
00:18:02,666 --> 00:18:05,041
Ginoza!

328
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:08,333
What is... going on?

329
00:18:08,416 --> 00:18:12,500
[KITAZAWA crying]

330
00:18:21,291 --> 00:18:23,666
[DOMINATOR] Crime Coefficient
is two hundred ninety-nine.

331
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:27,166
The target's Threat Judgment
has been reappraised.

332
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:30,791
Enforcement mode:
Non-Lethal Paralyzer.

333
00:18:30,875 --> 00:18:32,416
Trigger safety released.

334
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:35,166
Aim calmly and
subdue the target.

335
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,708
This is justice.

336
00:18:44,208 --> 00:18:45,583
[KITAZAWA falls on ground]

337
00:18:46,583 --> 00:18:48,625
[AKANE inhales]

338
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:50,666
[shaky exhale]

339
00:18:53,875 --> 00:18:58,041
[AKANE] It was a team effort!
Thank you all for your help!

340
00:19:00,125 --> 00:19:01,625
You know that an
enforcement target's

341
00:19:01,708 --> 00:19:04,125
Crime Coefficient
almost never decreases.

342
00:19:04,208 --> 00:19:06,625
In fact, I'd say it's
practically unheard of.

343
00:19:06,708 --> 00:19:10,000
[MIKA] And yet your strategy was
to gamble on it happening here.

344
00:19:10,083 --> 00:19:11,916
Sibyl had made a decision.

345
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:14,500
That creep didn't
deserve to draw breath!

346
00:19:14,583 --> 00:19:16,458
But you--

347
00:19:16,541 --> 00:19:18,041
Bought time.

348
00:19:18,125 --> 00:19:20,166
In the end, Sibyl
reversed that initial,

349
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:22,041
hasty assessment.

350
00:19:22,125 --> 00:19:24,375
Which is good, because
we still need to find out

351
00:19:24,458 --> 00:19:26,458
how he was able to
make all of those bombs

352
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:28,208
while keeping his Hue clear.

353
00:19:28,291 --> 00:19:32,458
I made a judgment call with
the future firmly in mind.

354
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:40,041
[MIKA] Inspector. On this one...

355
00:19:40,125 --> 00:19:42,000
you're flat-out wrong.

356
00:21:13,208 --> 00:21:20,500
♪

357
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,458
It's a... Holo?

358
00:21:23,541 --> 00:21:25,791
[FEMALE HOLOGRAM] So naïve.
Just because something is

359
00:21:25,875 --> 00:21:30,000
fabricated doesn't necessarily
negate its existence.

360
00:21:30,083 --> 00:21:32,541
You failed to recognize that.

361
00:21:34,625 --> 00:21:37,291
[SHISUI gasps]

362
00:21:40,708 --> 00:21:42,458
[MAN] Which is why...

363
00:21:46,916 --> 00:21:48,541
I am here.

364
00:21:48,625 --> 00:21:50,666
[DOMINATOR] Crime
Coefficient is forty-eight.

365
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,708
Target is a
registered Inspector.

366
00:21:52,791 --> 00:21:55,291
Warning: Any rebellious
conduct by an Enforcer

367
00:21:55,375 --> 00:21:58,125
will be recorded and
reported to headquarters.

368
00:21:59,916 --> 00:22:01,916
[YAMATOYA yells]

369
00:22:04,083 --> 00:22:06,041
[SHISUI] You can't.

370
00:22:17,875 --> 00:22:22,375
[AKANE] So, it was a
new beginning for me.

371
00:22:22,458 --> 00:22:24,416
The start of
my own personal battle

372
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:26,916
to decide who I really am.

